{"id": "1443139660967841854", "channel_id": "1443139660967841854", "type": 0, "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "author_bot": false, "content": "Video: Corposant, equipped with Wanda's WoD Queen's Edict, plays 2 Pilots, triggering Queen's Edict to increase Corposant's Aliemus by 8, twice. Then Corposant plays Lightning Retribution, it enters Ultra Space, triggering Queen's Edict correctly, and the next Pilot played does not trigger Queen's Edict.\n\nTheory:\nI believe Queen's Edict is checking __not__ whether a played card *enters* Ultra Space, but whether it *attempts* to enter Ultra Space.", "timestamp": "2025-11-26T07:21:47.413000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-11-26T21:02:59.190000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1443139661420560417", "filename": "ScreenRecording_11-25-2025_23-10-41_1.mov", "content_type": "video/quicktime", "size": 6453138, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1443139660967841854/1443139661420560417/ScreenRecording_11-25-2025_23-10-41_1.mov?ex=69ff894b&is=69fe37cb&hm=df2089a0a151d93861826e35047fe84b5a639bd789d00da30fdf9a208fe3532a&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1443139660967841854", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「Processing」Corposant Pilots trigger Queen's Edict Aliemus increase repeatedly", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
